General Info

        [yellowbal.gif] Club repeater call K2BNL, Calling frequency:
            442.400 MHz, PL=114.8

        [yellowbal.gif] Address:

        Brookhaven National Laboratory Amateur Radio Club
            PO Box 201
            Upton, New York 11973-5000

          [yellowbal.gif] Monthly meetings are on the last Thursday of the
          month at noon local time (EST5EDT) usually in Berkner Hall
          (cafeteria) or the Recreation Building. All members are
          encouraged to attend. Laboratory personnel are also invited.
